entries.title_d: Transport Jabba's gifts to the residents of Dathomir, watch out for pirate activity; most notably the Death Watch
entries.title: Dathomir System: Transport Jabba's Gifts - Part II
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Beissa: < \#pcontrast1 Two down, take the last package to an Inquisition contact.  Expect them to be difficult, the Imperials love to put on a show. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel here to meet up with your contact
entries.quest_location_d: Rendezvous points off of normal trade routes
entries.quest_dock2_d: Pull up next to the craft and use the /dock command to transfer your cargo
entries.hello_d: Who are you?! Are you the delivery ship? We cannot stay here long!
entries.found_loc_d: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Second rendezvous location locked in. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Excellent! This is a fabulous prize, my friend! Tell Jabba that we are open to his requests... whatever they may be.
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile activities have ceased. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1  Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Arrived at designated rendezvous location. \#pcontrast3 >
